## Vấn đề chính

### 1. ❌ Framework Leak — "investigation" 8 lần

`anti_framework_leak` được cập nhật **SAU** pipeline run này. Rule cũ chỉ nói "tên framework không xuất hiện" — không cấm vocabulary leak.

| Lần | Câu |
|-----|-----|
| 1 | Ch01: "This **investigation** will open seven case files" |
| 2 | Ch03: "our **investigation** now moves to..." |
| 3 | Ch04: "our **investigation** now ascends..." |
| 4 | Ch05: "our **investigation** now turns to..." |
| 5 | Ch06: "our **investigation** turns to..." |
| 6 | Ch07: "our **investigation** now travels west..." |
| 7 | Ch08: "our final **investigation** escalates..." |

> **Status**: ✅ Fixed by updated `anti_framework_leak` + WORD VARIETY rule

### 2. ⚠️ Structure không follow — 3/7 chapters

Ch02 (assigned mythbuster) vẫn dùng standard: Evidence → Mainstream → Counter → Questions. Writer prompt nói "FOLLOW the assigned structure" nhưng không đủ mạnh.

**Root cause**: Writer nhận structure name nhưng style guide `{style_json}` vẫn chứa framework steps "Hồ Sơ Điều Tra" → AI default về framework steps thay vì chapter structure.

> **Fix cần thêm**: Reinforce trong writer prompt: *"The `chapter_structure` OVERRIDES the framework's default steps. If assigned 'the_mythbuster', you MUST use the Mythbuster flow, NOT the framework's generic step order."*

### 3. ⚠️ Closing Ch02 sai — assigned physical_consequence nhưng viết rhetorical

Ch02 outline: `closing_type: physical_consequence`
Ch02 actual: Kết bằng 3 câu hỏi tu từ

> **Fix cần thêm**: Add enforcement: *"CRITICAL: You MUST end with the assigned closing_type. Writing rhetorical questions when assigned cold_fact/physical_consequence/irony is a STRUCTURAL FAILURE."*

### 4. ⚠️ Transition template lặp

6/7 body chapters mở bằng: "From [ch trước], our investigation now [verb] to..."

> **Status**: ✅ Partially fixed by WORD VARIETY rule. Cần thêm rule cấm template cụ thể.

